{"tid":2269943,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"預咗俾人屌 但係希望嗰位攬炒巴可以睇吓 不如開一間香港人嘅保險公司","createTime":"2020-11-03T18:53:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-03T19:57:53.000Z","uid":370186,"like":10,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2b2f1d284519bc7dffa22aa7b17bb08c9da7d4c3","tid":2269943,"uid":370186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T18:53:20.000Z","msg":"我想問吓你眾籌收咁多錢<br />\n點解唔直接建立一間香港人嘅保安公司<br />\n點解仲要用啲錢去打國際線？<br />\n<br />\n只有武力先係可以保障和平嘅資本<br />\n<br />\n你可以係外國建立一間保安公司<br />\n招聘香港人流亡嘅手足令到佢哋有工作嘅地點<br />\n可以請啲退休軍人 等佢哋嚟教 就好似歐洲啲保安學院咁樣<br />\n跟住可以承接唔同嘅保安任務 等個班人有經驗<br />\n<br />\n我想講真正嘅復國 唔係靠人哋去幫助<br />\n你哋成日用嚟打飛機嘅以色列 佢哋係用血汗去守護佢哋嘅家邦<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CHEc6YSF9R5/?igshid=r7ak0ov799qe\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCHEc6YSF9R5%2F%3Figshid%3Dr7ak0ov799qe&d=AZYGjn5ll7vy7cK20AVbo0pSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=404024c0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCHEc6YSF9R5%2F%3Figshid%3Dr7ak0ov799qe&h=062048fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CHEc6YSF9R5/?igshid=r7ak0ov799qe</a><br />\n<br />\n香港人講獨立已經講咗好耐 希望你哋可以踏出第一步 <br />\n<br />\n希望嗰位攬炒巴<br />\n唔好再寄望喺各國之間嘅權力鬥爭<br />\n而係寄望係自身香港人身上 只有自己足夠強大 咁就唔需要俾人可憐<br />\n<br />\n願意戰死嘅人唔多，但亦都唔少 <br />\n我哋只係爭一個機會，一個拉近武力差距嘅機會<br />\n<br />\n時代正在逐漸瘋狂<br />\n我們的命運都與時代革命交織<br />\n無人能置身事外<br />\n唯有以戰止戰  以死換生<br />\n<br />\n當一切落幕之時<br />\n還望能與爾等一同再三回味<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qEgT8Z0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqEgT8Z0.jpg&h=0f44b52b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n順帶一提嚟緊嘅11月11日 唔係一個俾你瘋狂購物嘅所謂光棍節 而係一個有特別價值嘅日子 你要給予為香港戰死嘅英靈最崇高嘅尊重"},{"pid":"8e8ced5901fb2179c81ad2b94f84427613170457","tid":2269943,"uid":370186,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T19:03:24.000Z","msg":"大家可唔可以幫手推到佢入嚟啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"042c843baf421ab438e1d8cdffa588f75edc3d2b","tid":2269943,"uid":69157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T19:10:35.000Z","msg":"保險定保安呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc105caa8b2088b64e931cb3c7cb0371b930b51b","tid":2269943,"uid":332769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T19:10:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c6f8ad766eb4b55752a811885e750c0bf15366df","tid":2269943,"uid":370186,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fc105caa8b2088b64e931cb3c7cb0371b930b51b","tid":2269943,"uid":332769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T19:10:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T19:13:22.000Z","msg":"仆街打錯字"},{"pid":"27c8616982a7f23deec8bfb5e8587fc930f5553a","tid":2269943,"uid":370186,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T19:13:47.000Z","msg":"咁多位我柒咗<br />\n係保安公司"},{"pid":"251d15b8237f25ae9206819dce3e1883ba9a9be6","tid":2269943,"uid":370186,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"042c843baf421ab438e1d8cdffa588f75edc3d2b","tid":2269943,"uid":69157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T19:10:35.000Z","msg":"保險定保安呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T19:14:19.000Z","msg":"乖你明白就好😘😘"},{"pid":"302909a5512e529d84f841430716ecb056a9337f","tid":2269943,"uid":291803,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"27c8616982a7f23deec8bfb5e8587fc930f5553a","tid":2269943,"uid":370186,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T19:13:47.000Z","msg":"咁多位我柒咗<br />\n係保安公司"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T19:27:52.000Z","msg":"見